Adapting the code you posted:

#!/usr/bin/perl

use strict; use warnings;

my @x = 1 .. 10;
my @y = grep { $_ % 2 } @x;

my %lookup = map { $_ =&gt; undef } @y;

for my $x ( @x ) {
    next if exists $lookup{$x};
    print "$x\n";
}

