answer:
Using Cordova >=3.0.0, you need to add the storage feature to your config.xml (app/res/xml/config.xml). E.g.

&lt;feature name="Storage"&gt;
    &lt;param name="android-package" value="org.apache.cordova.Storage" /&gt;
&lt;/feature&gt;

